message.body: From hann this morning, ugh i dunno what to think: I know its late but happy birthday. I got food poisoning and have been out of it. I don't want you thinking I don't care. I love you and we all still miss you.
It means let's be friends. If you want to fuck thats cool too. I don't want to be your bf though
Right? Or what do you think that means??
Oh my god I didn't even think about whAt it means.. I have no clue how it makes me feel.
I'm angry sad and maybe a little happy that he hasn't forgotten me. And that I didn't call him phew.
But I feel kind of numb
Yeah! Good job on not calling him! Whew!
